webscaff installation
================================================


Python ``setuptools`` package is required to install webscaff.


Use the following command line to install webscaff from sources directory (containing setup.py):

    easy_install .

or

    python setup.py install


Alternatively you can install an up-to-date version of webscaff from PyPI:

    easy_install webscaff


Note: `easy_install` is bundled with ``setuptools``.
